      <h3>Title II Policy</h3>
           <p> It is the policy of AT Products LLC that all customers, partners, etc. shall not be discriminated against to sex, race, color, national origin, religion, or handicap and that no customer, or any other person will be subject to discrimination.</p>
      <h3>Title VII Policy</h3>
     <p> It is the policy of AT Products LLC that all employment opportunities will be offered without regard to sex, race, color, national origin, religion, or handicap and that no employee, or any other person will be subject to discrimination. We will accommodate religion practices dependent on employees.</p>
